slides.title: Number Types
slides.content:
**Natural:** 1, 2, 3...
**Whole:** 0, 1, 2, 3...
**Integer:** ...-2, -1, 0, 1, 2...
**Prime:** Divisible by 1 and itself only
**Composite:** More than 2 factors

slides.title: Divisibility
slides.content:
**2:** Last digit even
**3:** Sum of digits รท 3
**5:** Last digit 0 or 5
**10:** Last digit 0
**11:** Difference of alternate digits sum รท 11
